suffered in the meantime.

Being able to walk to get food is the biggest quality of life improvement I’ve had in some time. Grocery store is like a 4 minute walk away instead of a 20 minute drive. I no longer have to do “the big shop” which I dreaded. I can simply grab a few things every couple days. I get more fresh air. I get more steps in. Saving on gas. Don’t have to sit in traffic. I’m home in like 12 minutes round trip.

I still have to drive for almost anything beyond groceries and fast food, but those alone have been huge. Even when I do have to drive, it’s less time on the road since I’m closer. I don’t think I’ll be able to give that up when it’s time to find a new place. Highly recommend.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/n6PsTVA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CamelEnamel]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good job young man</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dqQMY73</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TJjhtdR.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Integrity.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/dqQMY73</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Kyzyl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Trans mice wont compeat in women sports !</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UVqgcvE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4c8ABIB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Trans mice even completly stone it wouldn't  cross my mind</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UVqgcvE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pentjotal]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Jackie destroyed the banana tree</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/60giab0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cxCOUEa.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/60giab0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Masodlextr]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Low battery notification</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/b2zdg0A</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7pW9eQW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/b2zdg0A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[redghost999]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>ice cream trucks in the hood hit differently</title><link>https://imgu